{"tid":1889083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】物流署口罩唔夠派 財庫局允各部門自行採購1,000萬元以下定單","createTime":"2020-02-20T13:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T16:05:55.000Z","uid":3399,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f93a86b6c63486cb23e6ae3acd8962bbfbda1a34","tid":1889083,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》獲悉，財經事務及庫務局前日（18日）向政府各部門發出通告，指隨著武漢肺炎疫情發展，政府內部對口罩需求提高，引述行政長官林鄭月娥及各司、局長上周三（12日）決議，政府物流署只會分發口罩予醫護、從事隔離措施人員、政治清潔工及院舍職員等，其他部門一律無份。通告指，財庫局現容許相關部門自行採購口罩，1,000萬元以下的定單可直接採購，毋須政策局批准。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200220&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60622603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200220%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60622603&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=d90ff062\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200220%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60622603&h=f7636a6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200220&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60622603</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解唔夠派又可以借畀巴士公司？"},{"pid":"88b99dcde23ae6c35417e1842ae24a523054046f","tid":1889083,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:48:24.000Z","msg":"呢招好撚毒<br />\n唔限價姐係托價令香港人買唔到"},{"pid":"000a1123bf379cc22bcb33c7990642b20ec678ad","tid":1889083,"uid":3399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"88b99dcde23ae6c35417e1842ae24a523054046f","tid":1889083,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:48:24.000Z","msg":"呢招好撚毒<br />\n唔限價姐係托價令香港人買唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"啲奸商直接賣哂畀政府，又可以高價，又可以成批搞掂唔洗煩，真係好撚賤，明明自己夠用都要同市民爭"},{"pid":"d4b7cfaab33414d89ffcee04a3a542d6ea0a4946","tid":1889083,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:08:27.000Z","msg":"1千萬任買比唔洗番工既公墓員<br />\n區